aRame

Rame stands for Ruby + Ajax + Mongrel + Erubis

It's a little server that handle the http request and return the 
result of a erb page trough the erubis handler

The handler is in Classes and trough him you can use your application. The GMethod.class containes the link to Handler that link to file. the file are stored in /m/. Inside them there are the value of the query to the server.

